Package com.eim.utility.statistics.runners

Class Summary
AbstractStatisticsRunner Abstract utility that launchs the computations according to a set a properties.
AbstractStatisticsWorker Abstract thread implementation that provides the basic features (start dates extraction, existing values, ...) for statistics computations.
ActivePortfoliosStatisticsRunner Implementation of AbstractStatisticsRunner for active portfolios
ActiveProductsStatisticsRunner Implementation of AbstractStatisticsRunner for active products
BenchmarkRelatedStatisticsWorker Implementation of AbstractStatisticsWorker for benchmark related statistics
ComputedStatisticsWorker Implementation of AbstractStatisticsWorker for non-benchmark related statistics
IndicesStatisticsRunner Implementation of AbstractStatisticsRunner for indices
InvestedChildrenFundsStatisticsRunner Implementation of AbstractStatisticsRunner for invested child funds
InvestedTopLevelFundsStatisticsRunner Implementation of AbstractStatisticsRunner for invested top-level funds
UserDefinedWorkingSetStatisticsRunner Implementation of AbstractStatisticsRunner for a user defined entity type and a user defined entity ids list
